arts.ttl: Strasbourg loanee Djordje Petrovic set to return to Chelsea and compete for No.1 jersey
arts.sum: Djordje Petrovic’s (25) loan move to RC Strasbourg Alsace from partner club Chelsea has been an undeniable success. The Serbian goalkeeper was, for a time, No.1 at Chelsea last season,…
